description: Ukraine-Russia War News LIVE Updates: The Russian invasion of Ukraine entered its seventh day on Wednesday, with fighting intensifying in Kyiv and in other big cities. Russia's defence ministry said it was planning to strike targets in Kyiv used by Ukraine's security service. Earlier on Tuesday, an Indian student lost his life in the shelling in Kharkiv. In a briefing, Foreign Secretary Harsh Vardhan Shringla said no more Indian nationals are left behind in Kyiv and emphasised the government's efforts to evacuate citizens from Kharkiv. Stay tuned for LIVE updates
